teps#interactive","content":"Give a step an `onPress` handler to make it navigable. Steps without `onPress` are inert."},"795":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-28","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#disabled","content":"A disabled interactive step is muted, removed from the tab order, and cannot be activated."},"796":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-29","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#hide-step-numbers","content":"Step numbers are prepended automatically. Set `hideStepNumbers` to omit them."},"797":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-30","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"Step numbers (`\"N. \"`) are prepended automatically — keep them where possible, as user testing shows people recognize the component better with them. Set `hideStepNumbers` to omit them."},"798":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-31","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"`orientation` switches between `horizontal` (accent bar on top) and `vertical` (accent bar on the leading edge)."},"799":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-32","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"`currentStep` is the single source of truth for the timeline. Omit it for a not-yet-started flow where every step is `future`; pass the step count for a fully completed flow where every step is `past`."},"800":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-33","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"`status` is independent of timeline and only controls the status icon and (for `error`) the accent bar color."},"801":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-34","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"Pass `className` to the container or an individual step to extend the styles."},"802":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-35","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#accessibility","content":"The container renders a `<nav>` landmark; set `aria-label` to name it (defaults to `\"Progress\"`)."},"803":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-36","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#accessibility","content":"Steps are an ordered list (`<ol>`/`<li>`) so assistive technology conveys position and count."},"804":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-37","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#accessibility","content":"The current step is marked with `aria-current=\"step\"`."},"805":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-38","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#accessibility","content":"Interactive steps are real buttons: focusable in the natural **Tab** order and activated with **Enter** or **Space**. Status icons are decorative (`aria-hidden`)."},"806":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-39","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#accessibility","content":"Focus is shown with a visible outline; disabled steps use `0.4` opacity and are not focusable."},"807":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-40","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#best-practices","content":"Drive the timeline from `currentStep` rather than styling individual steps."},"808":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-41","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#best-practices","content":"Provide `onPress` only for steps a user can actually navigate to; leave it off for display-only steps."},"809":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-42","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#best-practices","content":"Keep titles short — they truncate with an ellipsis when space is tight."},"810":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-43","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#best-practices","content":"Always give the container an `aria-label` that describes the flow (e.g. `\"Checkout progress\"`)."},"811":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-44","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#troubleshooting","content":"**No step is highlighted:** `currentStep` is omitted, negative, or out of range. Set it to the active step's 0-based index."},"812":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-45","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#troubleshooting","content":"**A step isn't clickable:** it has no `onPress`, so it's inert by design. Add `onPress` to make it interactive."},"813":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-46","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#troubleshooting","content":"**Titles overflow:** that's expected — titles truncate. Shorten the title."},"814":{"id":"/docs/components/radio","page_id":"/docs/components/radio","type":"page","content":"Radio","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/radio"},"815":{"id":"/docs/components/radio-0","page_id":"/docs/components/radio","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/radio","content":"Accessible radio button